#: ../maps/brothers_lair_fire_hall.txt:366
msgid ""
"\"Today Pompeii got a little over-excited to meet me and blew himself up. So "
"I had to go into the caves and catch myself a NEW antlion burster. Again. I "
"think I'm going to name this one 'Krakatoa'. ~Vesuvvio (the Destroyer)\""
msgstr ""
"\"Chaill Pompeii a cheann an-diugh 'gam tadhal is spreadh e. Mar sin, bha "
"agam ri dol dha na h-uamhan agus spreadhadair biastaige ùr a ghlacadh ann. A-"
"rithist. Cha chreids mi nach cuir mir \"Cracatoa\" air an fhear seo. "
"~Beniamin Teine (am Milltear)\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:8
