msgstr "Talla Deighe nam Bràithrean"

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:287
msgid "Suspicious Bookcase"
msgstr "Preas-leabhraichean amharasach"

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:295
msgid ""
"\"When we could no longer stand the idiotic practices of our master, I "
"hatched a plan to kill him. My brothers agreed the deed had to be done.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Nuair nach b' urrainn dhuinn cleachdaidhean amaideach ar maighstir "
"fhulaing tuilleadh, innlich mi plana gus a mharbhadh. Dh'aontaich mo "
"bhràithrean rium gun robh feum air a' ghnìomh seo.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:305
msgid ""
"\"In accordance with our plan, G. asked the old fool to teach him about the "
"preparation of corpses in the later stages of decay. Naturally, the corpse "
"in question was a cleverly disguised bomb made by V.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Dh'fhaighnich G. a-rèir ar plana dhan bhodach amaideach an "
"dh'ionnsaicheadh e dha mu ullachadh nan corp air an crìonadh. Gu nàdarra, "
"cha b' e ach boma an riochd cuirp a bh' ann air a dhèanamh le B. gu seòlta.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:314
msgid ""
"\"My brothers and I wandered around for a few days. In an incredible stroke "
"of luck, we encountered a master necromancer who, seeing the marks of "
"banishment on our foreheads, took us as his apprentices.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Chaidh mi fhìn 's mo bhràithrean 'nar taistealaich greis. Nach sinne a bha "
"fortanach gun do thachair sinn air marbh-dhraoidh maighstir a mhothaich "
"comharraidhean an fhògraidh air ar leth-chinn is a ghabh sinn mar "
"fhoghlamaichean.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:316
msgid "Bookcase"
msgstr "Preas-leabhraichean"

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:324
msgid ""
"\"We grew swiftly under the tutelage of the necromancer. The more we "
"learned, the more we realized we could do better than the short-sighted git."
"\""
msgstr ""
"\"Dh'fhàs sinn gu luath fo ionnsachadh a' mharbh-dhraoidh. Mas as motha a "
"dh'ionnsaicheadh sinn 's ann nas soilleire a dh'fhàs e 'nar beachd gum biodh "
"sinn na b' fhearr dheth às aonais a' chrògaire a bhiodh goirid 'na lèirsinn."
"\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:334
msgid ""
"\"My brothers V. and G. used to go to a wizard's academy with me. We were "
"top students until one day V. killed another student in a spontaneous fit of "
"rage.\""
msgstr ""
"\"B' àbhaist do mo dhà bhràthair B. is G. a dhol gu acadamaidh dhraoidhean "
"còmhla rium. Bhios sinn 'nar sàr-oileanaich mus do mharbh B. oileanach eile "
"air bhoile latha a bha sin.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:344
msgid ""
"\"Naturally, V. was expelled for his crime. It was foolish of us, but G. and "
"I decided to defend our brother. We were expelled too. The wizards magically "
"marked us with a sign of banishment on our foreheads so that no wizard would "
"dare teach us.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Fhuair B. a' bhròg air sàilleibh eucoir mar a shaoileadh tu. Ged nach robh "
"sin glic, thug mi fhìn is G. romhainn ar bràthair a dhìon. Fhuair sinn a' "
"bhròg cuideachd. Chuir na draoidh comharran nam fògarrach air ar leth-chinn "
"ach nach dùraigeadh draoidh sam bith ar teagasg.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:354
msgid ""
"\"G. suggested that each of us should take one of the halls in the old "
"necromancer's lair.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Mhol G. gun gabhadh gach fear dhuinn aon dhe na tallaichean san "
"àite-còmhnaidh aig an t-seann mharbh-dhraoidh.\""

#: ../maps/brothers_lair_ice_hall.txt:364
msgid ""
"\"It's days like today that make me wonder if I should go a step further and "
"eliminate V. and G. too... they're getting on my nerves. ~Scathelocke\""
msgstr ""
"\"'S ann air làithean mar a tha seo gum bi mi a' cnuasadh am bu chòir dhomh "
"cur às dha B. agus G. cuideachd... tha iad a' cur dragh orm. ~Dubhghlas\""

