#: ../maps/cave1.txt:462
msgid ""
"These goblins have captured a human trader.  Human bones are carefully "
"arranged around the pillar in preparation for a goblin ritual."
msgstr ""
"Tha na bòcain seo air fear-malairt daonna a ghlacadh. Tha cnàmhan daonna air "
"an sgeadachadh mun cholbh gus deas-ghnàth nam bòcan ullachadh."

#: ../maps/cave1.txt:469
