#: ../npcs/guill.txt:1
msgid "Guill, Scribe of the Order"
msgstr "Guill, sgrìobhaiche an Òrduigh"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:15
msgid "Chat"
msgstr "Cabadaich"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:18
msgid ""
"I am Guill, a scribe with the Order. I am grateful you've come -- we are "
"short on trained warriors due to the call-to-arms in Ancelot."
msgstr ""
"'S mise Guill, sgrìobhaiche an Òrduigh. Tha mi taingeil gun tàinig sibh -- "
"tha gaisgich air an trèanadh a dhìth oirnn on a chaidh airm a thogail ann an "
"Ainsealot."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:19
msgid "Why is the Order interested in these ruins?"
msgstr "Carson a tha ùidh aig an Òrdugh air an làrach seo?"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:20
msgid ""
"What the locals call the Goblin Warrens is actually the entrance to a grand "
"underground fortress known as Averguard Keep. This site is sacred to our "
"order. Our primary mission is to cleanse the evil from this place."
msgstr ""
"Chan e ach slighe a-steach do Dhaingean Geàrd na h-Aibhne a tha san àite air "
"a chuireas a' mhuinntir ionadail am Broclach Bhòcan. Tha an làrach seo "
"naoimh dhan òrdugh againn. Is am prìomh-mhisean againn an àite seo a "
"ghlanadh on olcas."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:23
msgid "Goblins Warrens"
msgstr "Broclach Bhòcan"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:28
msgid ""
"The goblins in the Warrens answer to a warlord named Ukkonen. Most goblins "
"are merely curious; this Ukkonen is bloodthirsty. Punish him for desecrating "
"this place. His lair is here in the Warrens."
msgstr ""
"Tha na Bòcainn sa Bhroclach fo thighearna-cogaidh air a bheil Caochladh. "
"Chan eil a' mhòrchuid a Bhòcain ach feòrachail; 's ann fuileachdach a tha an "
"Caochladh. Peanasaichibh e airson tàmailt a chur air an àite seo. Tha an t-"
"àite-còmhnaidh aige sa Bhroclach seo."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:31
msgid "Ukkonen Search"
msgstr "Lorg Caochladh"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:34
msgid "Ukkonen's lair is somewhere here in the Goblin Warrens."
msgstr "Tha àite-còmhnaidh Chaochlaidh àiteigin ann am Broclach Bhòcan seo."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:37
msgid "Ukkonen Defeated"
msgstr "Chuir thu ruaig air Caochladh"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:44
msgid ""
"Ukkonen is defeated -- I sensed a calm in this place the moment you ended "
"him. Take this reward for your bravery."
msgstr ""
"Tha Caochladh air cheannsachadh -- Mhothaich mi sìth san àite seo cho luath "
"'s an do chuir sibh gu bàs e. Gabhaibh an duais seo airson ur gaisgeachd."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:47
msgid "Averguard Chronicles"
msgstr "Eachraidh Geàrd na h-Aibhne"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:51
msgid ""
"The Averguard left a set of Chronicles detailing their final era. One volume "
"is missing. I've searched this entire area except for Ukkonen's lair. If you "
"find the book please return to me."
msgstr ""
"Dh'fhàg Geàrd na h-Aibhne leabhraichean eachdraidh mun linn deireannach aca. "
"Tha iom-leabhar a dhìth. Tha mi air an àite seo a rannsachadh gu lèir ach "
"àite-còmhnaidh Chaochlaidh. Ma lorgas sibh an leabhar, an toir sibh air ais "
"dhomh e?"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:52
msgid "I'll keep an eye out for it."
msgstr "Bheir mi sùil a-mach air a shon."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:63
msgid ""
"You found this tome in Ukkonen's lair? Most excellent -- I feared this "
"volume was lost. With it we can piece together the true history of this "
"keep. I just need a moment to study..."
msgstr ""
"An do lorg sibh an leabhar seo ann an àite-còmhnaidh Chaochlaidh? Glè mhath "
"-- Bha mi fo amharas gun deach e air chall. 'S urrainn dhuinn fìor-"
"eachdraidh an daingein a choileanadh le seo. Chan fheum mi ach greis gus "
"sùil a thoirt air..."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:66
msgid "Averguard Keep"
msgstr "Daingean aig Geàrd na h-Aibhne"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:70
msgid ""
"This tome confirms what we know of Averguard Keep -- it crumbled against the "
"plague many centuries ago. But not all of the infected were destroyed. It "
"appears many undead where locked away in hopes that a cure would be found."
msgstr ""
"Tha an leabhar seo a dhearbhadh an eòlais againn mu Dhaingean Geàrd na "
"h-Aibhne -- Chaidh e a-bhàn fon phlàigh o chionn linntean. Co-dhiù, cha "
"deach a h-uile duine air an robh an galar a mhilleadh. A rèir coltais, "
"chaidh iomadh closach a ghlasadh a-steach, an dòchas gun rachadh leigheas a "
"lorg."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:71
msgid "Why were the undead spared?"
msgstr "Carson a chaidh na closaich a leigeil mu rèir?"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:72
msgid ""
"I don't know, but we should investigate. Head into the Atrium, then the "
"Averguard Prison. Search for a key to access the sealed areas of the Keep."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil fios agam, ach bu chòir dhuinn seo a rannsachadh. Rachaibh a-steach "
"dhan cheàrnag is an uairsin dha Tholl-dubh Geàrd na h-Aibhne. Lorgaibh "
"airson iuchair gus na raointean glaiste dhen daingean inntrigeadh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:79
msgid ""
"I have the prison key. The old prison warden carried it on his person -- he "
"was infected, haunting the depths of the Prison."
msgstr ""
"Tha iuchair an tuill-dhuibh agam. Bha neach-glèidhidh an tuill-dhuibh 'ga "
"chumail -- ghabh e an galar, a' tathach doimhne an tuill-dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:85
msgid ""
"A true shame that he was infected.  Well, now that we have the Averguard "
"Key, the depths of Averguard Keep are open to us. The Order thanks you."
msgstr ""
"'S truagh gun do ghabh e an galar. Nise, on a tha Iuchair Geàrd na h-Aibhne "
"againn, tha doimhne Daingean Geàrd na h-Aibhne fosgailte dhuinn. Tha an t-"
"Òrdugh a' cur taing dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:88
msgid "Burial Chamber"
msgstr "Seòmar adhlacaidh"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:93
msgid ""
"There is one place within the Keep that no living being has seen for "
"centuries: the burial chamber behind Averguard Temple. From the Atrium you "
"can access the Temple. Use your key to enter the Burial Chamber."
msgstr ""
"Tha àite san daingean nach fhaca duine beò fad linntean: an seòmar "
"adhlacaidh taobh thall Teampall Geàrd na h-Aibhne. 'S urrainn dhuibh an "
"teampall inntrigeadh on cheàrnag. Cleachdaibh an iuchair gus faighinn a-"
"steach dhan t-seòmar adhlacaidh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:94
msgid "Who is buried there?"
msgstr "Cò chaidh adhlacadh an-siud?"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:95
msgid "The powerful leader of the Averguard -- Sir Evan Maddox."
msgstr ""
"An ceannard cumhachdach air Geàrd na h-Aibhne -- Ridire Eòghann an Lighiche"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:100
msgid "Key to Burial Chamber"
msgstr "Iuchair an t-seòmair adhlacaidh"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:104
msgid "I tried the key on the Burial Chamber door but it would not open."
msgstr ""
"Dh'fheuch mi an iuchair air doras an t-seòmair adhlacaidh ach cha do "
"dh'fhosgail e."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:105
msgid ""
"It must be sealed by powerful magic. There was only one sorceror of "
"Averguard with that kind of power - Professor Langlier. Search through his "
"collection to find a way into the Burial Chamber. Enter the Academy through "
"the Atrium."
msgstr ""
"Feumaidh gun deach a ghlasadh le draoidheachd chumhachdach. Cha robh ach aon "
"draoidh aig Geàrd na h-Aibhne aig a bhiodh a leithid cumhachd - an t-Ollamh "
"Mac an Truisg. Rannsaichibh an cruinneachadh aige ach an lorg sibh dòigh gus "
"dol a-steach dhan t-seòmar adhlacaidh. Rachaibh a-steach dhan acadamaidh "
"tron cheàrnag."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:106
msgid "As you wish."
msgstr "Le 'r toil."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:107
msgid ""
"I must admit jealousy -- I have dreamed many years of seeing the old volumes "
"there, but it is simply too dangerous yet."
msgstr ""
"Feumaidh mi aideachadh gu bheil am farmad orm -- Bu mhiann leam na seann "
"leabhraichean an-siud fhaicinn o chionn bliadhnaichean mòra ach tha e ro "
"chunnartach fhathast."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:116
msgid ""
"I am back from the Academy. Langlier was rags and bones, yet still a "
"powerful mage. He wore this symbol."
msgstr ""
"Tha mi air ais on acadamaidh. Cha b' e Mac an Truisg ach cnàmhan is "
"rabhlagan ach bha e fhathast 'na dhraoidh cumhachdach. Bha an samhla seo air."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:120
msgid ""
"Fate has delivered this talisman to you. With it and the Averguard Key, you "
"have the ability to open the Burial Chamber. Read these runes aloud at the "
"sealed door and the path will be opened."
msgstr ""
"Thug an dàn an seun seo dhuibh. Bidh an comas agaibh gus an t-seòmar "
"adhlacaidh fhosgladh leis an t-seun is Iuchair Geàrd na h-Aibhne. Leughaibh "
"an rùn-sgrìobhadh os àrd aig an doras glaiste is thèid an t-slighe fhosgladh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:128
msgid ""
"My worst fear is come alive. Just as with the Warden and with Professor "
"Langlier, Sir Evan Maddox himself was inflicted with undeath. If we are to "
"reclaim the Keep, you must defeat him. The Order will reward you "
"magnificently for this service. But be prepared -- not even undeath will "
"limit Maddox's zeal. Enter the Burial Chamber and allow him redemption."
msgstr ""
"Thàinig an t-eagal as motha a bh' agam gu bith. Tha Ridire Eòghann an "
"Lighiche fhèin a' fulang le neo-bhàs mar a tha an neach-glèidhidh is an t-"
"Ollamh Mac an Truisg. Feumaidh sibh ruaig a thoirt dha ma tha sinn airson an "
"daingean a ghabhail air ais. Ach thoiribh an aire -- cha chuir eadhon an neo-"
"bhàs stad air dìoghras an Lighiche. Rachaibh a-steach dhan t-seòmar "
"adhlacaidh is thoiribh saorsa dha."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:131
msgid "Maddox Defeated"
msgstr "Chuir thu ruaig air Eòghann an Lighiche"

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:142
msgid ""
"You have risked much for the Order. Take this final reward, as your mission "
"here is complete. The grip of necromancy over Averguard Keep is broken -- in "
"time the remaining undead will pass over into death."
msgstr ""
"Mheantairig sibh mòran às leth an Òrduigh. Gabhaibh an duais dheireannach "
"seo on a tha am misean agaibh an-seo coileanta. Chan eil Daingean Geàrd na "
"h-Aibhne fo mharbh-draoidheachd tuilleadh -- Caochlaidh na closaich a tha "
"air am fàgail rè àm."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:143
msgid "Thank you Guill. I am glad to be of service."
msgstr "Tapadh leibh, a Ghuill. Tha mi toilichte gun tug mi cobhair dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/guill.txt:148
msgid ""
"It is still dangerous here, but with Maddox defeated his followers will soon "
"find rest."
msgstr ""
"Tha e fhathast cunnartach an-seo, ach on a chaidh an Lighiche a "
"cheannsachadh gheibh an luchd-leantainn aige fois shìorraidh a dh'aithghearr."

#: ../npcs/kayl.txt:1
msgid "Kayl, Alchemist"
msgstr "Cail, cumasgair"

#: ../npcs/kenrik.txt:2
msgid "Kenrik, Trade Guild"
msgstr "Cenrig, comann malairt"

#: ../npcs/lorund.txt:1
msgid "Lorund, Smith"
msgstr "Lorund, gobha"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:2
msgid "Martigan, Overseer"
msgstr "Martagan, fear-amhairc"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:13
msgid ""
"Welcome to my mines, stranger. If you have the back for it, I've got the "
"work."
msgstr ""
"Fàilte dha na mèinnean, a choigrich. Ma tha an druim agaibh, tha obair agam "
"dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:14
msgid "I heard you might have something more interesting."
msgstr "Chuala mi gun robh rudeigin na b' inntinniche agaibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:15
msgid ""
"Ah, you're the adventurer? If you seek out danger you're in the right place. "
"We had two guards stationed here; both were recalled to Ancelot. Now we're "
"vulnerable."
msgstr ""
"An sibhse am baoghlair? Ma tha sibh a' sireadh cunnart, seo an t-àite "
"dhuibh. Bhiodh dà fhreiceadan againn an-seo; chaidh an dithis aca a ghairm "
"air ais gu Ainsealot. Tha sinn so-leòinte a-nis."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:19
msgid "Goblin Camp"
msgstr "Campa nam bòcan"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:22
msgid ""
"We're having problems. Goblins. All the noise from our mining is drawing "
"their attention. We can't have them thinking we're easy prey."
msgstr ""
"Tha duilgheadasan againn. Bòcain. Tha fuaim na mèinne againn 'gan tadhal. "
"Cha bu chòir iad a bhith dhen bheachd gum biodh sinn 'nar ìobairtean furasta."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:26
msgid ""
"Attack their encampment up river from here. 20 gold now, 80 more when you "
"return."
msgstr ""
"Thoiribh ionnsaigh air a' champachadh aca suas na h-aibhne on a sheo. Bheir "
"mi 20 òr dhuibh an-dràsta is 80 a bharrachd nuair a thilleas sibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:29
msgid "Goblin Camp Search"
msgstr "Rannsaich campa nam bòcan"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:32
msgid ""
"The goblins have an encampment up the river from here on the west side. "
"Clear them out and I'll pay you 80 gold."
msgstr ""
"Tha campachadh nam bòcan taobh an iar suas na h-aibhne on a sheo. Glanaibh e "
"is bheir mi 80 òr dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:35
msgid "Rilrak Defeated"
msgstr "Chuir thu ruaig air Riolrag"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:42
msgid ""
"Unfortunate work, but my workers will sleep safe tonight. Here's your reward."
msgstr ""
"Seo obair mhì-shealbhach ach gheibh an luchd-obrach agam cadal sèimh a-"
"nochd. Seo ur duais."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:47
msgid ""
"A member of the Order passed through our camp a few days ago. He left for "
"the tower ruins in Ydrakka Pass."
msgstr ""
"Thàinig ball an Òrduigh tron champa againn o chionn beagan làithean. Dh'fhàg "
"e gus dol a làrach an tùir air Bealach Iodraca."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:50
msgid "Rotten Tower"
msgstr "Tùr lobhte"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:53
msgid ""
"This region was once well guarded. There are watch towers positioned "
"throughout these plains, but most are abandoned and crumbling now."
msgstr ""
"Bhiodh an sgìre seo 'ga dhìon gu math uair. Tha tùir freiceadain air feadh "
"na machrach seo ach chaidh a' mhòrchuid dhiubh a thrèigsinn is tha iad a' "
"dol a-bhàn a-nis."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:54
msgid ""
"I need someone to inspect the outpost tower in White Winds, south west of "
"the Frontier Plains. Let me know if goblins have found their way inside."
msgstr ""
"Tha cuideigin a dhìth orm gus sùil a thoirt air tùr a' ghearasdain ann an "
"Gaoithean Geala gu iar-dheas air a' mhachair crìche. Innisibh dhomh ma "
"fhuair bòcain a-steach."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:58
msgid "Rotten Tower Search"
msgstr "Rannsaich an tùr lobhte"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:61
msgid ""
"Search for the abandoned tower southwest of the Frontier plains. The lands "
"around there are called White Wind."
msgstr ""
"Lorgaibh airson an tùr air thrèigsinn gu iar-dheas air a' mhachair crìche. "
"'S e Gaoithean Geala a tha air an dùthaich mu thimcheall."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:64
msgid "Rotten Tower Found"
msgstr "Lorg thu an tùr lobhte"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:67
msgid ""
"There are plenty of goblins in the White Winds area, but not near the tower."
msgstr ""
"Tha grunn mhath bhocan ann an sgìre nan Gaoithean Geala ach cha tig iad "
"faisg air an tùr."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:68
msgid "Are you sure? Did you look inside the tower?"
msgstr "A bheil sibh cinnteach? An deach sibh a-steach dhan tùr?"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:69
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Uill..."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:75
msgid ""
"There are plenty of goblins in the white winds area, but not near the tower."
msgstr ""
"Tha grunn mhath bhocan ann an sgìre nan Gaoithean Geala ach cha tig iad "
"faisg air an tùr."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:77
msgid "I saw no signs of goblins through the locked iron grate door."
msgstr ""
"Chan fhaca mi sgeul air bòcain o thaobh a-muigh an dorais clèithe iarainn "
"dhùinte."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:79
msgid "Good! Have this small reward."
msgstr "Glè mhath! Seo duais beag dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:84
msgid "Mineshaft"
msgstr "Sloc mèinne"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:87
msgid "So how's the mining business?"
msgstr "Ciamar a tha a' mhèinnearachd a' dol?"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:88
msgid ""
"Not good at all. While I was digging, my pickaxe scraped a skull that was "
"wedged in the rock wall. Before I knew it, the nasty thing started moving "
"and a whole body emerged. Now that thing is in there, preventing any more "
"mining."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil gu math idir. Nuair a bha mi a' tochladh, sgrìobh a' phiocaid agam "
"claigeann a bha air gèinneadh sa bhalla cloiche. Mun canadh tu deis-dè, "
"thòisich an rud uabhasach seo air gluasad is thàinig corp gu lèir a-mach. "
"Tha an rud a tha seo a-staigh an-siud a-nis is a' cur bacadh air tochladh "
"sam bidh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:89
msgid "Kill that skeleton for me, and I'll make it worth your while."
msgstr "Ma mharbhas sibh an cnàimhneach air mo shon, bheir mi duais dhuibh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:97
msgid ""
"Please take care of that skeleton. Work in the mine can't continue otherwise."
msgstr ""
"An dèan sibh a' chùis air a' chnàimhneach? Chan urrainn dhan obair sa mhèinn "
"a leantainn air adhart mar a thà."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:100
msgid "Skeleton Defeated"
msgstr "Chaidh ruaig a thoirt air a' chnàimhneach"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:104
msgid "I've defeated the Reanimated Skeleton."
msgstr "Cheannsaich mi an cnàimhneach air ath-bheòthachadh."

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:105
msgid ""
"Excellent work! As promised, here's a little something for your troubles."
msgstr ""
"Math dha-rìribh! Mar a gheall mi dhuibh, seo rudeigin airson ur n-obair."

#: ../npcs/nerin.txt:1
msgid "Nerin, Bowyer"
msgstr "Nerin, ceàrd-bhoghachan"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:1
msgid "Statue Guardian (Fire)"
msgstr "Geàrd ìomhaighe (teine)"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:11
msgid "Who goes there?"
msgstr "Cò th' ann?"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:12
msgid "I came here to kill lots of monsters."
msgstr "Thàinig mi an-seo gus cur às dha torr bhiastan."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:15
msgid "Intruder! You shall not interrupt the masters' work!"
msgstr "A shlaighteir! Cha chuir thu stad air obair a' mhaighstir!"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:21
msgid "Vesuvvio."
msgstr "Beniamin Teine."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:22
msgid ""
"...Are you feeling alright, Master Vesuvvio? You did not refer to yourself "
"as \"the Destroyer.\""
msgstr ""
"...A bheil sibh gu math, a Mhaighstir Bheniamin? Cha do chuir sibh \"am "
"Milltear\" oirbh."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:23
msgid ""
"Have your brothers been teasing you about your real name being Stootley "
"again?"
msgstr ""
"A bheil do bhràithrean a' tarraing asad a-rithist gur e Seoc an t-ainm a th' "
"ort dha-rìribh?"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:24
msgid "Er, no. It's all right. I'm Vesuvvio the Destroyer."
msgstr ""
"Uill... chan eil. Tha sin ceart gu leòr. 'S mise Beniamin Teine am Milltear."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:27
msgid "Then welcome, Master Vesuvvio, may you enjoy your destruction tonight."
msgstr ""
"Mar sin, fàilte a Mhaighstir Bheniamin, gun gabhadh sibh tlachd às ur "
"milleadh a-nochd."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:28
msgid "(This Vesuvvio guy sure is strange...)"
msgstr "(Tha an duine Beniamin ud caran neònach...)"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_fire.txt:32
msgid "Welcome, Master Vesuvvio, may you enjoy your destruction tonight."
msgstr ""
"Fàilte a Mhaighstir Bheniamin, gun gabhadh sibh tlachd às ur milleadh a-"
"nochd."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_ice.txt:1
msgid "Statue Guardian (Ice)"
msgstr "Geàrd ìomhaighe (deigh)"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_ice.txt:12
msgid "Uh... a lone adventurer?"
msgstr "À... baoghlair aonaranach?"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_ice.txt:21
msgid "Scathelocke."
msgstr "Dubhghlas."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_ice.txt:24
msgid "Welcome, Master Scathelocke."
msgstr "Fàilte, a Mhaighstir Dhubhghlais."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_wind.txt:1
msgid "Statue Guardian (Wind)"
msgstr "Geàrd ìomhaighe (gaoth)"

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_wind.txt:12
msgid "A friend of the masters."
msgstr "Caraid a' mhaighstir."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_wind.txt:21
msgid "Grisbon."
msgstr "Gaothraidh."

#: ../npcs/statue_guardian_wind.txt:24
msgid "Welcome, Master Grisbon."
msgstr "Fàilte, a Mhaighstir Ghaothraidh."
